Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Anna.\NThe wind is getting colder, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? She's rather unfriendly today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just coming home, Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All the restaurants\Naround here are already closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the hotel, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone on this street… For some reason,\Nthey act as if they know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They all call me Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Suk, a serial murder suspect,\Nis being treated here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,there's not a single cop\Nor patrol car here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'll check things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, regardless of what's up,\NI'll need to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a hint of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're caring\Nfor an injured man by the name of Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan Suk. He's a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was one of the injured men\Nat the building on Bruno Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, one of those homeless men\Nwho got into a big fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Homeless men? In a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered what\Nthey were saying on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be what the story is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what room are those men in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They were pretty badly injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but they were transferred\Nafter being treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Transferred?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. All six of them\Nwere loaded into ambulances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Six? That's the number of men\Nwho attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Suk?\NJan Suk, the police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the men\Nbrought to us had been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then is there any record of a man\Nnamed Jan Suk being brought here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Documents and a tape\Nrelated to Kinderheim 511…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Petrov was\Nthe former director of Kinderheim 511
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and was operating\Nan unlicensed orphanage in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave them to me just before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And who wants them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure who wants them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but those former\NCzechoslovakia secret police people are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to get their hands on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the documents and tape now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not with me.\NSomeone else is holding onto them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was for those
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that Suk was seriously injured\Nand then abducted from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what those people will do\Nto Suk to get what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in those documents\Nand on that tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The documents are research reports\Nfilled with technical terminology
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and a list of names.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't look at them closely\Nand only listened to part of the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's on the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A recording of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The child is being questioned.\NI think he was drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When asked his name, he said it was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinderheim 511…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Research reports…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the tape now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep this businesslike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay with going along,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no reason for you to get\Ninvolved in this as well, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some questions of my own for\Nthe former Czechoslovakia secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is it you're trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:07:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the real question is whether or not we'll\Nbe able to reason with these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you brought us here\Nto treat us to dinner, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He was probably a big shot in\Nthe former Czechoslovakia secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw him in an old\Nnewspaper article.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Captain Karel Ranke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we finally meet the top brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am terribly sorry for\Nthe rough treatment by my subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a slip-up in the chain of command\Nthat led to this unintended situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We have become deeply misunderstood\Nnot only by you but by all of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're seen as a gang of murderers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's being taken care of\Nat one of our hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,His life is not in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't just some misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Our people did not kill\Na single person in all these incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that blonde woman\Ntaking orders from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's not part of\Nour organization at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, she's causing us lots of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not trying to kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A German associate of ours wants\Nthose documents and tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in\Nserious negotiations with Petrov.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was killed just as we began.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a lot of money involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is all about business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply want to talk business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll exchange Suk\Nfor that tape and those records.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not have that kind of negotiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of thing\Nshould never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what would happen\Nif that kind of thing got out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of thing\Nshould never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time\Nfor discussion of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with\Nthis negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I am from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I come from Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that I was 14 then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That was 30 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NProbably when I was seven or eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then around 1963, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In the early 60's,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ostensibly stationed\Nat the Czechoslovakian embassy in Berlin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but worked as an intelligence officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a younger sister\Nwho married a German.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She and her husband tried\Nto defect over the Berlin Wall
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but were shot and killed\Nduring their attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Their son, that boy, remained behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I signed the papers that put him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I was told,\Nit sounded like a magnificent place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the ideal educational facility
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that would raise children with\Na checkered past to become
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the elite backbone\Nof the future communist party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I signed the papers that put him\Ninto Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no memories\Nof my time there or from before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to make money off\Nof something so reprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to sell
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the research data obtained\Nfrom experiments on your own nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gone off-topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like us to continue\Nthis negotiation in a businesslike way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll end things here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can reach an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them where they'd like to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's most important\Nright now is saving Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he'll release Suk\Nif we give him what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cocoa…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our weekly serving of cocoa…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved that serving of cocoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I had a fever\Nand was laid up in the infirmary,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,he brought me his cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He brought me his own cocoa\Neven though he loved it so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never had cocoa\Nas delicious as that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to do something\Nto return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Just remember me."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a popular thing for us to do then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We would tell our friends about ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,\Nbut during the creepy lessons,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the memories of ourselves\Nslowly faded away day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We realized we'd even forget\Nour own names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why… we had\Nour friends remember who we were for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved cocoa! He loved drawing pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But he hated preserving insects\Nbecause it would kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The most fun he had was when\Nhe went to the forest with his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They caught lots of butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But he released them from\Nthe insect cage just before they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,His dream was to become an entomologist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,His…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,His name was…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolf Reinhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping secrets from him is a no-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,People can become…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever they want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the street here…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the scenery…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And this sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You know this door too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,These stairs too…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer,\Nafter thinking about it all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, that tape and those documents\Nreally aren't any of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we won't have time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears they want\Nto get on with the negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The former Czechoslovakia secret police\Nhave come all the way here to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you thought it over carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm not giving you\Nthe tape or the research papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't care\Nwhat happens to Detective Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens to Suk,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the tape and documents\Nwill disappear forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Threats like that will get you nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am willing\Nto let you listen to the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll forget about trying to sell it\Nto that German associate of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like to listen to the tape\Nin private, then I'll gladly let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I think you should listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of your nephew\Nwho you sent to Kinderheim 511,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you should listen to the voice of\Nthe boy named Johan that's on that tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the deal you're offering me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're sitting here doing this,\Nsomeone could get killed over that tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize how many\Nof your Czechoslovakia secret police
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,have been killed in these incidents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the person\Nwho wants that tape most of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the person\Nwhose voice is on that tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your German associate told you\Nwhat's on that tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it he told you you'd find?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster's identity." That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to get\Nyou people mixed up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But before anyone else gets killed,\NI need to tell you about what happened…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this Johan came here to Prague\Nin search of his roots?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He may have come here to erase them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you people do 15 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A mother and child lived near\NCedok Bridge in Michalska.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,One day,\Nthey were abducted by the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When you took Johan\Nfrom the building with the three frogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what did you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,THREE FROGS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These stairs…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My big brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He was dragged away down these stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Admittedly, in my position at the time,\NI knew everything that went on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But three frogs?\NAbduction of a mother and child?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In truth, there were some things\Nthat I never heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The things a certain man did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew what department\Nof the secret police
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he was assigned\Nto or who he took orders from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He freely detained many people,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but for some reason,\Nhe never had to report it to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what he was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was only a mere lieutenant,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but he was given\Na luxurious mansion to work out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. He was called\Nthe "Man of Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he had anything\Nto do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a very refined and quiet man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He never wore a uniform\Nand loved having tea and cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:20:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I don't know\Nif that is his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He also had a pen name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He also wrote picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this door scare you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I… read a picture book inside here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone opened this door…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture books?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They were creepy picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One was called "The Nameless Monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was here\Nreading a picture book,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but the person who opened\Nthe door and came back…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I come back to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by: Brian Athey
